Class ManagedLoadTimer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.camel.support.ServiceSupport
      • org.apache.camel.support.TimerListenerManager
        • org.apache.camel.management.ManagedLoadTimer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable, CamelContextAware, NonManagedService, Service, ShutdownableService, StatefulService, StaticService, SuspendableService

    public class ManagedLoadTimer
extends TimerListenerManager
implements NonManagedService
    The TimerListenerManager used for tracking load statistics.

    From Camel 2.13 onwards the ManagedLoadTimer is only enabled if ManagementStrategy.isLoadStatisticsEnabled() is enabled.
